Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.29,0:01:44.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看啊 那个转校生就是传说中的…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.09,0:01:47.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,杀了自己父亲的?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.13,0:01:59.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,照到了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.72,0:02:01.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,照得非常清楚噢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.86,0:02:04.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过 这样做没关系吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.62,0:02:05.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事没事
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.10,0:02:08.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,反正她以前也遇到过同样的事
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.64,0:02:10.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.76,0:02:31.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,救赎 荣耀和力量
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.41,0:02:34.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,皆属于我神
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.92,0:02:37.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他的裁决是真实而正确的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.39,0:02:40.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,玛丽亚大人
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.38,0:02:53.35,Title,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第五话　斗士无惨
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.88,0:03:02.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,宝物在哪里
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.70,0:03:03.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,宝物?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.11,0:03:05.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是指龙玉吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.37,0:03:30.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我问你在哪里
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.75,0:03:39.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这正是所谓的尘归大地 红玉上青天
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.58,0:03:43.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这孩子是真心要杀我
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.45,0:03:45.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你知道吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.02,0:03:50.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人只要失去全身三分之一的血液就会死哦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.87,0:03:53.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是玛丽亚大人说的嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.37,0:03:57.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,玛丽亚大人… 是谁
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.62,0:04:01.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有人教过你吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.11,0:04:06.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,向别人提问之前 要先回答对方的问题
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.18,0:04:09.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在在提问的是我哦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.53,0:04:17.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,糟了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.47,0:04:20.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就告诉你吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.78,0:04:23.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,龙玉是不会交给任何人的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.94,0:04:54.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回答我吧 你是什么人
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.02,0:04:56.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么要找龙玉
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.26,0:05:02.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不说的话 就会这样死掉哦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.71,0:05:08.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,玛...玛丽亚大人
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.61,0:05:18.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是对我的考验吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.56,0:05:22.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还是…惩罚呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.48,0:05:30.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 如果这样能够更接近你一点的话
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.57,0:05:38.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我会欣然…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.11,0:05:40.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要再无谓地挣扎了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.78,0:05:42.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接受的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.74,0:05:45.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的玛丽亚
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.86,0:05:49.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,司马懿大人
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.41,0:05:58.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没关系的 不用这么害怕
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.57,0:06:01.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,马上就会让你解脱了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.30,0:06:15.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是许昌学院初中部的典韦吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.43,0:06:23.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谁
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.27,0:06:28.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,典韦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.83,0:06:33.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这家伙很难对付哦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.00,0:06:36.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然是这样吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.75,0:06:40.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即使是一无所知 被人操纵的人偶
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.72,0:06:43.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也不能容忍其进一步的暴行
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.48,0:06:46.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不可原谅
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.22,0:07:17.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么变成这样还要战斗呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.89,0:07:23.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是为了忠诚于把你培养成杀人机器的主人吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.05,0:07:26.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这份精神非常美丽
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.52,0:07:28.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且比什么都强大
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.34,0:07:29.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.63,0:07:33.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,玛丽亚大人
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.38,0:08:10.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我把你们的同伴放下了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.46,0:08:12.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,赶快给她疗伤吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.74,0:08:24.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吕蒙
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.44,0:08:28.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了 公谨
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.77,0:08:32.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小蒙
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.86,0:08:38.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,醒了吗 吕蒙
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.69,0:08:44.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,乐就 这里是?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.04,0:08:46.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是周瑜的家
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.63,0:08:48.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小蒙 你去哪了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.80,0:08:51.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才想终于见到你了 却是遍体鳞伤
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.10,0:08:54.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吕蒙 是谁干的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.81,0:08:55.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.32,0:08:57.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,外表看上去还是个孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.75,0:09:00.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但却充满了杀意
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.62,0:09:03.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我为什么会在这里
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.10,0:09:07.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像是什么人把你放在门口了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.28,0:09:10.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们一直在找你哦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.29,0:09:15.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊 我们还去了成都学园呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.31,0:09:18.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吕蒙竟然突袭这里
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.45,0:09:19.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不可能的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.78,0:09:21.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果相信你所说的话
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.32,0:09:24.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就是吕蒙的个人行动了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.40,0:09:27.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不知道吕蒙的目的是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.52,0:09:32.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 现在的南阳没有和成都开战的意思
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.25,0:09:37.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吕蒙
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.48,0:09:40.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你到底打算在成都干什么
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.33,0:09:43.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且 整整一个月去哪里了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.15,0:09:47.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吕蒙 是连我们都不能告诉的事情吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.35,0:10:08.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,三国时代的英雄 孙策伯符
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.80,0:10:12.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,由于自己的英勇结果失去了性命
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.15,0:10:16.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们的首领拥有其灵魂
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.23,0:10:19.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,会走上相同道路也是必然的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.74,0:10:25.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要抑制龙只有一个方法 龙玉
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.55,0:10:26.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,龙玉?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.26,0:10:28.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的有这种东西吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.21,0:10:31.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,信不信是你的自由
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.40,0:10:33.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是什么人
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.11,0:10:34.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么要告诉我
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.42,0:10:38.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们同样拥有被许昌所打败的过去
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.34,0:10:43.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想 打倒许昌是我们彼此共通的夙愿
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.46,0:10:44.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以才告诉你
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.82,0:10:51.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是　孙策 刘备 曹操
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.66,0:10:55.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也就是统领三国时代的英雄
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.24,0:10:59.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,相传在他们幻化成龙同时重生之时
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.84,0:11:03.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,龙玉真正的力量就能够发挥出来
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.64,0:11:07.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请告诉我们 吕蒙
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.00,0:11:11.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那和南阳的命运有关系吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.94,0:11:14.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,龙会召唤龙
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.78,0:11:18.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看来你也暗藏着龙啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.03,0:11:23.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,龙玉呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.23,0:11:25.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,龙玉?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.25,0:11:28.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我身上什么也没带吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.38,0:11:30.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是 什么也没有
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.38,0:11:35.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是那家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.64,0:12:04.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.70,0:12:42.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是那家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.72,0:12:43.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是那家伙把龙玉拿走了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.05,0:12:46.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不可以动 吕蒙
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.03,0:12:52.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恐怕是把我送来这里的人
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.17,0:12:56.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吕蒙 那个龙玉到底是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.82,0:13:01.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小蒙
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.66,0:13:02.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小蒙
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.88,0:13:04.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伯符 冷静点
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.26,0:13:07.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还是请先生来看一下比较好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.18,0:13:10.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剑伤加上刺伤啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.99,0:13:14.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对方显然是要杀吕蒙
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.29,0:13:16.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这么过分的事是谁干的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.58,0:13:22.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么一定要杀小蒙呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.04,0:13:23.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太过分了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.28,0:13:26.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这种事 不可原谅
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.01,0:13:29.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,孙策 你…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.13,0:13:30.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伯符 不可以
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.51,0:13:32.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不妙
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.99,0:13:33.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伯符
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.09,0:13:46.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是危险啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.80,0:13:48.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真会给人添麻烦啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.18,0:13:52.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没想到龙的觉醒会在战斗以外的地方出现
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.02,0:13:54.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以前也有过这样的事吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.38,0:13:57.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,逐渐增多了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.13,0:13:59.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只有伯母能控制住
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.51,0:14:09.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,勾玉的命运之潮不容分说地吞噬他们
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.77,0:14:10.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,并将他们带走
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.15,0:14:13.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 说不定
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.02,0:14:18.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这些孩子可以越过这一狂潮
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.44,0:14:22.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没错 一定能够越过
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.22,0:14:24.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我必须相信
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.48,0:14:30.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就像过去我相信你那样
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.72,0:14:43.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底发生什么事了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.18,0:14:47.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也不知道典韦能不能复原啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.50,0:14:50.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.06,0:14:54.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只有这么一句话啊 明明那么疼爱她的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.93,0:14:55.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接下来就拜托了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.82,0:14:57.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个… 等等
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.17,0:15:08.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,结果 典韦和我都不过是她的道具而已啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.08,0:15:23.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,惇{\r}啊 我们到底是什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.84,0:15:28.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,孟德
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.12,0:15:32.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能够维持自我的时间逐渐减少了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.69,0:15:39.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不久我就会被1800年前的魔王连心都取代了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.30,0:15:44.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所谓的斗士 本来就是被取代了的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.72,0:15:49.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果我完全变成了魔王
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.96,0:15:51.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个时候 惇…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.53,0:15:56.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可能连你也会杀的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.96,0:16:06.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,孟德 你以前说过吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.63,0:16:11.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果助我高升的话 天下也就跟着来了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.90,0:16:17.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我啊 很期待和你一起到手的天下哦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.58,0:16:22.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且 如果被你干掉了也不坏啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.08,0:16:31.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,惇{\r} 听到这话我就放心了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.56,0:16:35.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要夺取我们的天下
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.50,0:16:39.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真正的战斗就从今天开始
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.70,0:16:42.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从今天开始?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.68,0:16:46.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.44,0:16:50.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有什么事吗 曹操
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.28,0:16:54.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那边还有夏侯惇{\r}大哥啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.46,0:16:58.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谁命令你攻击孙策伯符了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.49,0:17:03.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有 我只是想帮助夏侯惇
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.79,0:17:06.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不记得拜托过你这种事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.51,0:17:18.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这种事不是结果一样就行了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.45,0:17:21.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当时要不是被夏侯惇{\r}阻止了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.14,0:17:24.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,孙策的首级就由我们…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.22,0:17:25.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已经够了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.13,0:17:27.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们已经没用了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.38,0:17:28.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回去
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.53,0:17:32.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别开玩笑了 曹操
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.52,0:17:36.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,乌丸高中确实是完全屈服于许昌了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.39,0:17:40.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 我们的心没有给任何人
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.76,0:17:47.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且 我们并不是放弃了天下
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.03,0:17:53.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,曹操算什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.81,0:18:03.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你要谈论天下吗 蜴顿
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.02,0:18:07.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能够谈论天下的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.51,0:18:10.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,除了我以外只有两个人
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.94,0:18:32.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果是你的话…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.44,0:18:35.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是曹操孟德的话…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.49,0:18:38.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也许真的能够夺取天下
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.37,0:18:47.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到那天为止 我惟有跟随你
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.90,0:18:52.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哪怕你成为了魔王
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.14,0:19:06.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下车吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.56,0:19:08.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,马上为您准备轮椅
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.47,0:19:10.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 不用了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.34,0:19:16.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,开车吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.48,0:19:17.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.21,0:19:36.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀哎呀 一个人在这里烦恼些什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.75,0:19:38.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,冰之军师大人
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.00,0:19:40.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是谁
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.22,0:19:42.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是张辽文远
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.54,0:19:46.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在许昌的新军师手下工作
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.39,0:19:46.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.53,0:19:48.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.46,0:19:54.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,1800年前打倒了那个诸葛军师的人
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.06,0:19:54.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你知道他的名字吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.84,0:20:01.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,司马懿仲达
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.51,0:20:04.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,继曹操孟德之后
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.09,0:20:07.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他终于作为许昌的第二位登场了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.59,0:20:11.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也就是说 你已经被解雇了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.30,0:20:20.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你这家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.84,0:20:24.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,至今为止辛苦你了 贾诩文和
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.00,0:20:27.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.22,0:20:31.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么郭嘉要对我隐瞒司马懿的存在
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.44,0:20:37.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,结果我从一开始就没有得到信任吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.86,0:20:42.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,无论是郭嘉还是曹操
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.75,0:20:50.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样的话 我不用顾虑任何人了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.37,0:20:54.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今后就用自己的手去把握
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.06,0:21:00.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这就是龙玉
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.81,0:21:02.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,干得好
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.33,0:21:04.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,愧不敢当
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.19,0:21:09.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,若不是吕蒙子明在与典韦的战斗中消耗了体力
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.93,0:21:12.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说不定被干掉的是我
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.08,0:21:14.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你说她的力量是龙吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.41,0:21:17.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这不是该由我下判断的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.92,0:21:21.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么并非军师的一介斗士 吕蒙
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.97,0:21:23.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,会有这样的力量呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.20,0:21:26.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有 先生有话要我转达
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.01,0:21:29.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是时候去会见伏龙了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.77,0:21:33.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伏龙…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.50,0:21:37.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诸葛孔明
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.85,0:23:14.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为了改变我们的君主 刘备玄德的命运
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.36,0:23:15.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,得到了龙玉
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.90,0:23:18.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 成都霸业尚缺少的是
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.23,0:23:20.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,飞舞于青天下的伏龙
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.90,0:23:21.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诸葛孔明
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.50,0:23:24.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在1800年前的赤壁
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.87,0:23:27.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为蜀国带来了胜利的天才军师
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.75,0:23:31.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 她足以成为引领我们的军师吗
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.62,0:23:33.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,关羽云长将用自己的双眼去确认
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.37,0:23:36.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下一集　一骑当千{\fnSimhei\fs25}Dragon Destiny
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.77,0:23:39.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第六话　伏龙逢着
